{"tid":1535046,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文：必要時要協助在台港人","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T08:24:11.000Z","uid":212626,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4967519055e764a3399e57b1c2219e4d25e9e251","tid":1535046,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"香港反修例風波惹來國際關注。台灣總統蔡英文在facebook發文，表示自己在聽取「香港情勢發展專案小組」報告後，作出四點指示，包括堅定支持香港的民主和自由，嚴正呼籲北京信守對香港高度自治的承諾，切勿以台灣、其他國家對香港民眾的關心，作為指控外力介入的藉口，<span style=\"color: red;\">強調台灣一如國際社會，必要時基於人道考量，對於在台港人會提供必要的協助，不會坐視</span>。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文又表示，陸委會和教育部會全力協助來台就學的港生，讓他們安心學業，也呼籲港府理解香港年輕人追求民主自由的初心，又說香港情勢已進入關鍵階段，國安及行政部門會緊盯香港的動態變化，協助台商及在港的台灣人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGW3Prw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGW3Prw.jpg&h=3bf1deb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e7%a8%b1%e5%8a%9b%e6%8c%ba%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e6%b0%91%e4%b8%bb-%e8%94%a1%e8%8b%b1%e6%96%87%ef%bc%9a%e5%bf%85%e8%a6%81%e6%99%82%e5%8d%94%e5%8a%a9%e5%9c%a8%e5%8f%b0%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba-187340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e5%258a%259b%25e6%258c%25ba%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25b0%2591%25e4%25b8%25bb-%25e8%2594%25a1%25e8%258b%25b1%25e6%2596%2587%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%25bf%2585%25e8%25a6%2581%25e6%2599%2582%25e5%258d%2594%25e5%258a%25a9%25e5%259c%25a8%25e5%258f%25b0%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba-187340&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDT1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=a1487dd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e7%a8%b1%e5%8a%9b%e6%8c%ba%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e6%b0%91%e4%b8%bb-%e8%94%a1%e8%8b%b1%e6%96%87%ef%bc%9a%e5%bf%85%e8%a6%81%e6%99%82%e5%8d%94%e5%8a%a9%e5%9c%a8%e5%8f%b0%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba-187340</a>"},{"pid":"2bf8be46b042914027f176e40287118b00aa4339","tid":1535046,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T